\is id ciṭitun bāreta gosṭi
\im \k lihi kītona porol: \k* yākob
\im \k lihi kīta sāl: \k* kiristu sakam lag-bag cālis siyunalte panas (45–50) sālkun naḍḍum lihi kiyval jargta.
\im \k muke gosṭi: \k* ad gaṭkate yākob inval porol veleṭirkun matta. vīrgaṭal vēr yākob yēsunor tamur āndur. yēsu pisi maneke, vēr yākob vōnga barosa irmaki bati, sāsi-nēṇḍta peje, vōr yēsu karalen bagavantanor mari āndur injer sūḍsi, kari kīsi barosa irtor.
\ip maraṭ taklibknaṅg pariksan vōrci mune tākteke, bagavantan poro karal barosa manta inval dusrurkun kare mānta. carcitur saṅga ani bahiḍur lōkur saṅga manval tarika sūḍsi, karal barosatun bārete kari kiya vaco. kiyvalik kāmk ani vaḍkvalik gosṭin hindal, karal barosa manta ki sele injer mākun kare mānta. karal barosatun bahan kari kiyana invaḍun bārete id ciṭitaga manta.
\iot baga batal manta
